text: Haha, ok yeah that would be really weird
I’m still so surprised we didn’t get an Energy-based/ adjacent legend in Kaladesh. Obviously it would be fairly linear deck-building, but that hasn’t stopped people before (and I like energy.)
Yeah, and I don't know that we'll get one even if we return to Kaladesh.
Hopefully people freaking out about narrow mechanic-focused commanders in C19 doesn't kill us getting those kinds of favors in the future.

And a return to Kaladesh is doubtful as well.

I will say, I wouldn’t want to see an Energy-focused precon deck. Make it Temur-Counters deck and make it one of the replacement commanders or something (if that was the direction they went.)

I agree, at least as a first time around. That said, I would actually welcome the Commander precons becoming hyper-focused as we keep seeing them year after year. I think it's a good niche for them to fill.
That would be sweet
